{"tid":1138662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[佃製作所][下町火箭]日本首次有民間自主研製的火箭，成功發射上太空。","createTime":"2019-05-04T16:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T18:16:52.000Z","uid":31637,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7913b7fa95fe496ff0528fd2d51e43e298352536","tid":1138662,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"稱為「MOMO」三號機的火箭，在當地清晨 5 時 45 分發射，實現預期目標，上到高空 113 公里。<br />\n<br />\n這是日本首次有民間自主研製的火箭，成功發射上太空。<br />\n<br />\n「MOMO」三號機長約十公尺，可以搭載 20 公斤重的觀測及實驗裝置。<br />\n<br />\n研發火箭的是北海道一間航天初創企業，前年和去年亦嘗試發射火箭，但失敗告終。公司期望到 2023 年能夠發射搭載小型衛星的火箭。<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2292963414076255/?__xts__[0]=68.ARDic9v8esLB7vRDMkGlrxSGLMn-sDXghcdEqg5_JsPIXmEn2aMKtBwnIqD6DPEIyyfTv2LHkhDWJUanE1xUt2LK_iRrWPGIOBshAQ8uXL0VozoGA2r7eg5p2PetxDNx47Bkn_V4S4-UNDA-chkDtPiMFEWzYJh23sxEtmz0qJhc2aWmPKMF0NoxuHATN48IVF-mwUkvnOgLQrvet2oTzZFhSSRbryERn0HaWxYxQ5X6OOQFb2ra2UblFfFZlTeN_1GfARGycg5nVDIzJwgmqVld8tW3hp-QMUfWKxpFeE9BNA5Aw38Ys2HrFLsr9AveCjvsi-o8-bbhUL5-7P1QSnYZW_I0zHFHuxxXz6T02gc9PKqg-QRXrDKd_2qXySwaKA&amp;__tn__=-R[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F2292963414076255%2F%3F__xts__%5B0%5D%3D68.ARDic9v8esLB7vRDMkGlrxSGLMn-sDXghcdEqg5_JsPIXmEn2aMKtBwnIqD6DPEIyyfTv2LHkhDWJUanE1xUt2LK_iRrWPGIOBshAQ8uXL0VozoGA2r7eg5p2PetxDNx47Bkn_V4S4-UNDA-chkDtPiMFEWzYJh23sxEtmz0qJhc2aWmPKMF0NoxuHATN48IVF-mwUkvnOgLQrvet2oTzZFhSSRbryERn0HaWxYxQ5X6OOQFb2ra2UblFfFZlTeN_1GfARGycg5nVDIzJwgmqVld8tW3hp-QMUfWKxpFeE9BNA5Aw38Ys2HrFLsr9AveCjvsi-o8-bbhUL5-7P1QSnYZW_I0zHFHuxxXz6T02gc9PKqg-QRXrDKd_2qXySwaKA%26__tn__%3D-R%5B%2Furl%5D&d=u%2FngHNJi%2FtIBC1CiWprX8UyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=c05f1873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/2292963414076255/?__xts__[0]=68.ARDic9v8esLB7vRDMkGlrxSGLMn-sDXghcdEqg5_JsPIXmEn2aMKtBwnIqD6DPEIyyfTv2LHkhDWJUanE1xUt2LK_iRrWPGIOBshAQ8uXL0VozoGA2r7eg5p2PetxDNx47Bkn_V4S4-UNDA-chkDtPiMFEWzYJh